
  Shedinja    Bug Type Pokémon

  SHEDINJA’s hard body doesn’t 
  move - not even a twitch.  In 
  fact, its body appears to be 
  merely a hollow shell.  It is 
  believed that Shedinja will 
  steal the spirit of anyone peering 
  into its hollow body from its 
  back. 
	Evolution Chain
      Nincada ► Ninjask

